org.apache.olingo.server.api.uri

Interface UriInfo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    UriInfoAll, UriInfoBatch, UriInfoCrossjoin, UriInfoEntityId, UriInfoMetadata, UriInfoResource, UriInfoService

    public interface UriInfo
extends UriInfoService, UriInfoMetadata, UriInfoResource, UriInfoBatch, UriInfoAll, UriInfoCrossjoin, UriInfoEntityId

    Object acting as general access to URI information extracted from the request URI.

    Depending on the URI info kind different interfaces are used to provide access to that information. Use method getKind() to obtain URI info kind information and to perform an appropriate cast.
